RULE SET 1
No voice chat channel hopping.
No annoying, loud or high pitch noises.
Reduce the amount of background noise, if possible.
Moderators reserve the right to disconnect you from a voice channel if your sound quality is poor ONLY if the users connecting prevents chat and or disrupts chat sessions with friends(mods who abuse this will be banned)
Moderators reserve the right to disconnect, mute, deafen, or move members to and from voice channels.
No command spam.
No macros.
No hacks.
No adding/changing/removing commands.
